# 🏡 EstateHub API

A full-featured **Real Estate Management REST API** built with **Node.js**, **Express**, **TypeScript**, and **MongoDB**. The system supports customers, agents, and administrators with authentication, property management, bookings, payments, messaging, notifications, analytics, and more.

---

# 🚀 Features

## 🔐 Authentication

* User Registration & Login
* JWT Authentication
* Role-based Authorization (Admin, Agent, Customer)
* Password Hashing using bcrypt
* Protected Routes

---

## 🏠 Property Management

* Create Property
* Update Property
* Delete Property
* Get All Properties
* Get Property Details
* Property Search & Filtering
* Property Approval System
* Image Upload (Cloudinary)
* Property Categories
* Property Views Counter

---

## ❤️ Wishlist

* Add Property to Wishlist
* Remove Property from Wishlist
* Get User Wishlist

---

## 📅 Booking System

* Create Booking Request
* Approve Booking
* Reject Booking
* Cancel Booking
* Complete Booking

---

## ⭐ Reviews & Ratings

* Add Review
* Property Rating Calculation
* Average Rating Updates Automatically

---

## 💬 Messaging

* Real-time Chat using Socket.IO
* Buyer ↔ Agent Conversations
* Message Read Status
* Unread Messages Count
* Typing Indicator

---

## 🔔 Notifications

* Real-time Notifications
* Booking Notifications
* Payment Notifications
* Property Approval Notifications
* Mark Notification as Read
* Notification History

---

## 💳 Payments

* Stripe Checkout
* Booking Payments
* Agent Subscription Payments
* Payment History
* Stripe Webhook Integration

---

## 📦 Subscription Plans

* Free Plan
* Pro Plan
* Premium Plan
* Active Subscription
* Cancel Subscription

---

## 📊 Admin Dashboard

* Dashboard Statistics
* User Management
* Property Approval
* Category Management
* Revenue Statistics
* User Growth Analytics
* Monthly Revenue
* Monthly Bookings
* Top Agents
* Top Properties

---

## 👨‍💼 Agent Dashboard

* Total Properties
* Pending Bookings
* Completed Bookings
* Earnings
* Unread Messages

---

